hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Hold the line, please safe sleeve cases As recently as August, a 20-year-old female experienced the ruthless nature of sharks, whilst snorkeling in a typical tourist destination of Hawaii. During the incident, her entire right arm was severed, and she died a week later from her injuries. The horrendous attack prompted authorities to immediately close several beaches, stretching one mile in either direction from the location of attack.
